HEADWORD: Obstetrics
<hw>Ob*stet"rics</hw> <pr>(⟦ocr⟧b*st⟦ecr⟧t"r⟦icr⟧ks)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Cf. F. <ets>obst⟦eacute⟧trique</ets>. See
<er>Obstetric</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The science of
midwifery.</def> <mark>[archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
